{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1696943469.952375", "card_id": "Q_625468460", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 151}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "国内成品油近 4 个月来首次下调，加满一箱油将少花 3.5 元，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "国家发改委发布通知，今天（10 月 10 日）24 时起，汽油下调 85 元 / 吨，柴油下调 80 元 / 吨。按一般家用汽车油箱 50L 容量估测，加满一箱 92 号汽油，将少花 3.5 元。据国家发改委价格监测中心监测，本轮成品油调价周期内（9 月 20 日—10 月 9 日）国际油价大幅震荡。平均来看，伦敦布伦特、纽约 WTI 油价比上轮调价周期略降 0.72%。国内成品油近 4 个月来首次下调 加满一箱油将少花 3.5 元"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-8b4d9f6a7257426ec71f8b91f595192f_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1190 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/625468460"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI7aGP6dnbvddUEAMaCTEwMTI3MjIwMyCQqpSpBjAAOL8BQAByCTYyNTQ2ODQ2MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1696943469.953365", "card_id": "Q_625266034", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 130}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "集团派来了一个年轻的，没有什么经验的小姑娘做总经理，我这个二把手应该如何面对接下来的工作？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我可能是总经理的首选人物，之前找我谈过但是我拒绝了。因为我自己不想接一个不盈利的项目。 没想到会派过来一个小姑娘。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d826950e6a4e9e25f5f6ecb47768b57e_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "281 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/625266034"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI7aGP6dnbvddUEAMaCTEwMTIyNzI1OCDo1o2pBjAAOJ4CQAFyCTYyNTI2NjAzNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1696943469.953733", "card_id": "Q_625441745", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839